node.text:
Let me take a Selfie!
When the location is as dope as this, who wouldn't want a picture. This is about an hour hike away from Khambachen towards Nupchu Pokhari. The perspective of the mountains change as we gain altitude and Mt. Khangchendzonga (kumbhakarna) looks massive compared to the other two mountains. When we were in Khambachen, they almost felt the same height.

Watch our Nupchu Pokhari video if you haven't already (link in bio)

Shot by @ashish.5tha
